n = int(input())
divisors = list(map(int, input().split()))

divisors.sort()

x = 1
y = 1

for i in range(0, n, 2):
    x *= divisors[i]
    y *= divisors[i+1]

print(x, y)

n = int(input())
divisors = list(map(int, input().split()))

x = 1
y = 1

for i in range(n):
    if divisors[i] == divisors[i+1]:
        x *= divisors[i]
        i += 1
    else:
        y *= divisors[i]

print(x, y)
